Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的村子与外面的世界隔绝\N过着自给自足的生活已经有400多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓夏至祭 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了迎接会在每个夏天归来的祖先的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.68,0:00:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并祈求他们保佑丰收的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典将开始于明天黎明 一直持续到晚上再结束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你们能留下参加完祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 那个玫瑰花窗和尖塔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像古画中的中世纪教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这边的墙也很古老啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这口井也岁数不小了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.48,0:00:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是狼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近的山中住着野狼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这个村子里住的是人而不是狼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么胡话 我们是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我族本身和外界的人类不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简 简直和柯蒂丽亚一摸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那时我还是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是记得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荷曼妮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪人柯蒂丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这个宅邸 对于这个村庄来说都是不可抹灭的灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荷曼妮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案件发生在狄奥多村长的书房里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:37.50,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,560)}夏祭降临的神谕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜里的12点女仆在书房……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 当时柯蒂丽亚只有15岁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我让她去更换水壶里的水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天也是如此 正好是12点整
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会知道“正好”12点整？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:04:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和其他人看到柯蒂丽亚正用钥匙进入房中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我看了一下怀表确认了下时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不知为何和我在一起的人对时间的证词完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入书房的柯蒂丽亚立刻尖叫着冲了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们慌忙赶了过去一看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄奥多村长被短刀刺中 已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何地上掉落许多金币
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金币？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 这个村子里并不使用金币这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常都是狄奥多村长集中保管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那夜开始柯蒂丽亚就发高烧卧病不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等她退烧后 继任村长的我就将她逐出了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐出村子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时她身上就只有一枚金币和一只行李箱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等她一离开村子 我们就收起了吊桥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个从没踏出村子半步且不谙世事的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难想象可以她能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪人不能留在村里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则会给村里带来灾难 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个柯蒂丽亚的女儿现在却在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说散步什么的 可是我们明明才刚来这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加真是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是去散步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谢尔吉斯的助手 我叫安普罗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是好奇为什么你的皮肤和头发颜色会与众不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然知道外面世界不全是金发……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加 帮帮我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你呢 有个地方希望你能带我去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽管吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对的 可以让我再摸摸这个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你喜欢 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂丽亚住过的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 就这样走掉了么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人要是被知道带我们来这里会出问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是里面什么也没有……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂丽亚小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和还是婴儿的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是柯蒂丽亚在15岁的时候被赶出这里的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人来过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且他带走了本来放在这里的某样东西 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对的 留下了柯蒂丽亚长大后的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个混沌指向何处？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄奥多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是前任村长的坟墓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.47,0:07:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能对坟墓做这么不敬的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂丽亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写下这个的人是柯蒂丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲果然是因为子虚乌有的罪名才被赶出村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的罪人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是维多利加的眸子似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是狼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我输给你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我钱我倒是可以考虑输给你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 电话怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米 米尔德丽特小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然电话的话 果然这边有通电吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 村长说他们是过着自给自足的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也觉得很不可思议 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一问那个奇怪的女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像他们暗地里有赞助者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞助者？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 名字是什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 叫布莱恩·罗斯可的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩·罗斯可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是离开村子到外面生活的村民子孙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前这个人就开给村子提供资金了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 牌玩腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 我们去看看教堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刚刚有狼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:10:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西 那个讨人厌的老头子会赶跑它们的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 我们那么走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又缠起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾丝啊花边之类的是在太多了拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩·罗斯可十年前来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他带着什么目的来村子的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了给村子通上电不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前 你想想 正是世界大战刚刚打响的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种时代到深山里给村子拉上电线有点太仓促了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也正和那张照片被拍下的时间相吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带来了洗澡用的热水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请加入一些冷水后使用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能洗澡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加 万一发生什么事叫我一声哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:10:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}洗…洗…澡 好喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}因为暖洋洋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 原来是在唱歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的维多利加好像又回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也稍微喘口气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.61,0:11:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 维多利加 你那边没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么吵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人试图借此吓唬我 为了让我离开这个村子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:11:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个村子给我一种讨厌的感觉 太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会保护我的 对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 这是红芜菁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个彩车 是冬之军的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬之军？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这广场上的男人们会演一出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏之军和冬之军战争的戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏之军会打倒冬之军的大将冬之男
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把车子点火烧掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们是来侮辱这村子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就赶快滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊 居然相信迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个阴暗的村子 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啦 要是现在被赶出村子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 那个 这家伙到哪都会和人吵架的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这就回房间吧 呐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙昨天晚上也在圣堂里闹事来着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们当着村民的面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把用来装饰的旧水壶扔进装着圣水的水缸里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 要做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟醉鬼还会有什么道理可讲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们还嘲笑说那种破烂东西居然还被看得那么重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明他们自己见到古董的时候也开心成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你 这是祭典的点心 帮你弄来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.35,0:14:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛 痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚兰先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说了那种话 果然还是挺喜欢这个祭典的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 这个有什么意义的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个就是安普罗兹先生吧 好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬之男 你就化为灰烬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是纸人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 让开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拿水来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚兰先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚兰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是事故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他想妨碍祭典被人和纸人换掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢尔吉斯大人 那是不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑娘们扔榛果的时候 这个年轻人正巧经过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广场上又聚着很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得要跟纸人调换是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多嘴是愚蠢者的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就这样终止祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们接下去还有教堂的仪式要举行 失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都死人了 居然还在继续祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很奇怪啊 这个村里的村民
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 维多利加？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会保护我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一弥先生 你也是来询问未来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？未来？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏之军胜利了 丰收也得到了保障
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个教堂的话 一直到晚上都不进行日常活动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为教堂连接着那个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来观看丰收的先祖会经过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 接近这边的先祖的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会借助于村长之口 来回答孩子们的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一弥先生 机会难得 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...那个... 我和维多利加...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...等一下 安普罗兹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那样的话 不需要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那女孩和你不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你想问什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上 我有个朋友...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今后 可以和维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在一起么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在数年之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会刮起一股震撼世界的飓风
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们的身体都太轻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你们会因为那风而天各一方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的心永远不会分开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天各一方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加 你也来这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你问了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会不会再长了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高 你这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在生什么气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 一声不吭就突然消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才都去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书房
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪人柯蒂丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄奥多大人就是这样被人从背后刺中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直刺那个短刀只能看见刀柄那么深
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄奥多大人是个成年人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而柯蒂丽亚是个15岁的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高的差距太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将短刀插在小孩够不着的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要深至只能看见刀柄的程度是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪人柯蒂丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那肮脏的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人另有其人 你也是这样想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧之泉开始诉说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的碎片 都已被重组了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.34,0:21:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被重组的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你知道谁是犯人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就算知道谁是犯人 我手上也没有证据
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.55,0:21:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼出现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算出了人命 就算狼也出现 夏至祭也不可以中断
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:21:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟上去 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经听不见狼的声音了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.80,0:22:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我射中一头了 安普罗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是第二个人了 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.73,0:24:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的罪孽在发出光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.10,0:24:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮过去的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.95,0:24:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 有种非常不祥的预感
